"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/acourtois/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9d0366c5cd45d3aebc64fae3fc5786ee5f156c8e9b48c014452e68dba1971eaa?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9d0366c5cd45d3aebc64fae3fc5786ee5f156c8e9b48c014452e68dba1971eaa?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/acourtois/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">acourtois</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 18, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It does exactly what I wanted.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A beautiful masonery gallery with Pinterest links!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Really Great, best I&#039;ve found!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ideahost/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b8bc39374331f8f0c61cd1e5d6791d50e0b85ce130678827cb0ba0c378ab0fd2?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b8bc39374331f8f0c61cd1e5d6791d50e0b85ce130678827cb0ba0c378ab0fd2?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ideahost/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ideahost</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 10, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Was using other gallery plugins, three in fact over the past few years. This one beats them, easy to use, easy user interface. Thanks a million!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works really well and is clearly strcuctured!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/anbamuc/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0552d55122474af271d8dc57c02a4d4e8ed199160448b9aff392eef590c79fcf?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0552d55122474af271d8dc57c02a4d4e8ed199160448b9aff392eef590c79fcf?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/anbamuc/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Andreas <small>(anbamuc)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 4, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I tried several addons until I found MODULA IMAGE GALLERY. Problem solved.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works Great, Good Support, Friendly Support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gerald2023/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2bfe52b0e1c02441700c57aa2bd64aed0cdbd23c7b111a77b1e49027e34ace95?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2bfe52b0e1c02441700c57aa2bd64aed0cdbd23c7b111a77b1e49027e34ace95?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gerald2023/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">gerald2023</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">août 22, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a freelancer, I purchased this plugin for a client who wanted to create her own image galleries. Modula worked well for the task, but the abundance of options was a bit overwhelming for my client. It\'s best to set up the gallery yourself or create a template gallery that can be duplicated and edited, making it easier for clients to manage.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The installation process wasn\'t straightforward and took some time to figure out. I had to uninstall and reinstall the plugin to get it fully functional. However, the overall experience was positive, and when I reached out to support, they were friendly and helpful.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In summary, Modula is a great tool, but the extensive options might be initially frustrating for you or your client. It would be helpful if they offered different views—beginner, intermediate, and advanced—so that clients aren\'t overwhelmed when they first click the \"edit gallery\" button. A beginner view could include basic settings like thumbnail size, gallery type, thumbnail gap, pagination type, and color. Just my thoughts.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Overall I would say that it could be more user friendly especially with the install, set up, and explanation of what an upgrade includes. I upgraded, then it did not work, then I had to uninstall and reinstall the plugin to get everything working. I looked at the site and it did not clearly state that I would get the slider gallery with the upgrade, so after upgrading I was confused, spent time researching, finally uninstalled and reinstalled and the new upgraded features started working.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the end, the friendly and helpful tech support was such a relief—they truly made the experience a pleasant one. However, I\'m not sure about their response times or if they tend to reply only during the night (for my timezone). It would be helpful if they could provide more information on this.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Free version generates good looking masonry galleries</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mattsson/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cfe305ce0855d92791f9cb4c737fce2b5f7b59f2ea8f37c22ecae096cf634da9?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cfe305ce0855d92791f9cb4c737fce2b5f7b59f2ea8f37c22ecae096cf634da9?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mattsson/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mattsson</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">août 15, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I like this gallery plugin a lot, because even the free version is capable of generating beautiful galleries that I like the look of:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>I like the look of the masonry gallery;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>It\'s easy to add a bunch of images to start a new gallery, then drag and drop to order them;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>I set the gutter to the default 10 pixels;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>I set the image size to \"medium,\" which I set in media manager to be 400 x 400 pixels.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>My tips on laying out an attractive gallery: I like \"automatic\" column type (fill each row edge to edge with images) and then I set row height to 250 pixels.  I set the aspect ratio of each image to match what I think is best for the content.  Then I order the images to achieve a pleasing look.  That is, avoid a row that\'s got just a couple of wide images, because that row will be really tall.  Set some portrait-oriented images to fall at the end of the row to keep the row to a moderate height.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The settings include whether or not to display the image title and the image caption. Keep in mind that the TITLE is displayed in the gallery page hover or not, while the CAPTION is displayed only on hover. You set the title and caption for each image in the gallery.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I used my theme\'s \"additional CSS\" to style the titles and captions: bold, centered text and add a semi-transparent background behind the text. In each gallery\'s settings you can set the font color and size for titles and captions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mylocaljames/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8f3e49b2b7e01ce791e172e57b2c091f581c6bf646e57f07ddb2babb15978619?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8f3e49b2b7e01ce791e172e57b2c091f581c6bf646e57f07ddb2babb15978619?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mylocaljames/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mylocaljames</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">août 9, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>good for use , it\'s easy</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Brilliant Support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alanrogers/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/64b36b1701e2b11a8d20a9661bd9fc0dd87e20a0f3dcfbc0f925e5e42798508d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/64b36b1701e2b11a8d20a9661bd9fc0dd87e20a0f3dcfbc0f925e5e42798508d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alanrogers/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">alanrogers</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">août 8, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I\'ve only been using the Modula Gallery plugin for a few weeks now and it\'s the first time I\'ve used such a plugin, which I only really purchased in order to watermark our website images.<br /><br />On a couple of occasions I\'ve had questions I needed to submit to the Support Team and on both occasions - firstly with Teo &amp;  secondly with Beatrice - I\'ve received support of the highest level. The functionality within the plugin is great too so I have no hesitation in recommending this product.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:148:\"The WordPress gallery plugin that&#039;s highly customizable &amp; you can use to impress your clients. Create beautiful image galleries in minutes.\";s:14:\"upgrade_notice\";a:1:{s:6:\"2.10.0\";s:142:\"<ul>\n<li>This update indroduces the control for upload position of new gallery images and several edit gallery layout improvements.</li>\n</ul>\";}s:11:\"screenshots\";a:20:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:77:\"https://ps.w.org/modula-best-grid-gallery/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=3095828\";s:7:\"caption\";s:36:\"Custom Grid – Freely resize images\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:81:\"https://ps.w.org/modula-best-grid-gallery/assets/screenshot-2-old.png?rev=3095828\";s:7:\"caption\";s:27:\"Custom Grid – Helper Grid\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:77:\"https://ps.w.org/modula-best-grid-gallery/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=3095828\";s:7:\"caption\";s:31:\"Back-end Options UI Walkthrough\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:77:\"https://ps.w.org/modula-best-grid-gallery/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=3095828\";s:7:\"caption\";s:40:\"Responsive galleries created with Modula\";}i:5;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:77:\"https://ps.w.org/modula-best-grid-gallery/assets/screenshot-5.