la888</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 22, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A simple plugin, but which solves so many headaches and helps customise your content order with an easy drag and drop. Thanks a lot to developers!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simple and perfectly working</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lucascn/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7e7efe49957d4467ff8c5f719234cfbbed958e5dbb2319a5a3db65fb47ba0017?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7e7efe49957d4467ff8c5f719234cfbbed958e5dbb2319a5a3db65fb47ba0017?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lucascn/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">lucascn</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 16, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I was asking myself if this will work with all custom posts types and other plugins that show the posts but it works perfectly, no complicated settings or configuration. Awesome thank you very much</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Sick.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tiltedchair/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/50049947be34e3f91c17109f165c7e0f2877d4bb374efd43d9683be6be37fffb?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/50049947be34e3f91c17109f165c7e0f2877d4bb374efd43d9683be6be37fffb?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tiltedchair/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tiltedchair</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 11, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Works just like it should. Minimal, useful, fabulous.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:167:\"Ordonnez les publications (articles, tous types de publications personnalisées) en utilisant un JavaScript triable par glisser-déposer. Aucune configuration requise.\";s:14:\"upgrade_notice\";a:0:{}s:11:\"screenshots\";a:3:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:76:\"https://ps.w.org/simple-custom-post-order/trunk/screenshot-1.png?rev=3202586\";s:7:\"caption\";s:41:\"Ordonner les publications personnalisées\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:76:\"https://ps.w.org/simple-custom-post-or