s-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/enzojchesterfield/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4415279b71dd563d15f734c80339984d760f21fd7804430b6d5a050b18243101?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4415279b71dd563d15f734c80339984d760f21fd7804430b6d5a050b18243101?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/enzojchesterfield/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">enzojchesterfield</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">septembre 10, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It works great and easy, I thought the won\'t let me do without paying but it\'s totally free.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent plugin for my Clients</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/karen-lewis/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a3a67981714921a80374b91a53d56b1fd3baf357c976934eb57270c97a415347?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a3a67981714921a80374b91a53d56b1fd3baf357c976934eb57270c97a415347?s=32&#03